Title: Designates a portion of the state highway system as the "Rockland County Clerk Paul Piperato Memorial Highway"
Summary: Designates a portion of the state highway system in the hamlet of New City, town of Clarkstown, county of Rockland, as the "Rockland County Clerk Paul Piperato Memorial Highway".
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to designating a portion of the state highway system as the "Rockland County Clerk Paul Piperato Memorial Highway"
